<section class="process" id="process">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span><span class="ml-en">The 48-hour build</span><span class="ml-es">El build de 48 horas</span></span>
    <h2><span class="ml-en">From brief to live site, <span class="accent">in three short steps.</span></span><span class="ml-es">Del brief al sitio en vivo, <span class="accent">en tres pasos cortos.</span></span></h2>
    <p><span class="ml-en">No project managers, no kickoff decks, no two-week discovery phase. You talk to Mike or Santiago, we build, you review, we ship.</span><span class="ml-es">Sin project managers, sin decks de kickoff, sin descubrimiento de dos semanas. Habla con Mike o Santiago, nosotros construimos, usted revisa, publicamos.</span></p>
  </div>

  <div class="process-grid">
    <div class="step now">
      <div class="num">1</div>
      <h3><span class="ml-en">The brief</span><span class="ml-es">El brief</span></h3>
      <p><span class="ml-en">A 30-minute call (or a WhatsApp thread). You tell us your hours, your menu, what makes your shop different. We capture photos, copy notes, brand colors.</span><span class="ml-es">Una llamada de 30 min (o un hilo de WhatsApp). Nos cuenta sus horarios, su menú, qué hace diferente su negocio. Capturamos fotos, notas de copy, colores.</span></p>
      <span class="when"><span class="ml-en">Day 1 · 30 min</span><span class="ml-es">Día 1 · 30 min</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="num">2</div>
      <h3><span class="ml-en">The build</span><span class="ml-es">La construcción</span></h3>
      <p><span class="ml-en">We design and code your site overnight. By the next morning you've got a staging link, real photos in place, real copy, ready to click through.</span><span class="ml-es">Diseñamos y construimos su sitio durante la noche. Al día siguiente tiene un link de staging, con fotos reales y copy listo para revisar.</span></p>
      <span class="when"><span class="ml-en">Day 2 · overnight</span><span class="ml-es">Día 2 · overnight</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="num">3</div>
      <h3><span class="ml-en">The review</span><span class="ml-es">La revisión</span></h3>
      <p><span class="ml-en">You walk through the staging link. Anything you want changed, we change. Same-day turnaround on every revision in week one (or two on Pro).</span><span class="ml-es">Recorre el staging. Lo que quiera cambiar, lo cambiamos. Cada revisión sale el mismo día durante la primera semana (o dos en Pro).</span></p>
      <span class="when"><span class="ml-en">Day 2-3 · same-day</span><span class="ml-es">Día 2-3 · mismo día</span></span>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="num">4</div>
      <h3><span class="ml-en">Launch</span><span class="ml-es">Lanzamiento</span></h3>
      <p><span class="ml-en">You pay the 70% balance, we point your domain, the site goes live. The 30-day money-back clock starts the moment your site loads at your URL.</span><span class="ml-es">Paga el saldo del 70%, apuntamos su dominio, el sitio queda en línea. La garantía de 30 días empieza apenas el sitio carga en su URL.</span></p>
      <span class="when"><span class="ml-en">Day 3 · live</span><span class="ml-es">Día 3 · en vivo</span></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

